column2: SELECT TOP # GAL.ObjID, SO.chunk, SO.ra, SO.dec,SO.z,PO.u,PO.g,PO.r,PO.i,PO.z,SO.specobjid from  SpecOBJ SO, galSpecLine LINE, Galaxy GAL, PhotoObjAll PO where SO.bestObjID= GAL.ObjID and LINE.specObjID = SO.specObjID AND SO.specObjID= PO.specObjID AND LINE.sii_#_flux ># AND LINE.sii_#_flux ># AND LINE.oiii_#_flux ># AND LINE.oiii_#_flux ># AND LINE.oiii_#_flux ># AND SO.z between # and # and SO.snMedian >#
